            "paragraph" : "Zumba is a fitness program that involves cardio and Latin-inspired dance. It was founded by Colombian dancer and choreographer Beto Pérez in 2001,[1] It currently has 200,000 locations, with 15 million people taking classes weekly, and is located in 180 countries.[2] [3]Zumba is a trademark owned by Zumba Fitness, LLC.  "
